"Gentoo Linux安全建议"("GLSA")是由Gentoo安全小组发布的关于Gentoo Portage树中的有漏洞的软件的通知。这些报告包含漏洞本身的信息，对Gentoo系统可能的影响，对外部信息(例如CVE)的引用，以及如何修复漏洞(多数情况下是更新或者升级一个或者多个软件)。

GLSA notifications are managed as XML files within the Gentoo repository (see {{Path|${[[portageq]] get_repo_path / gentoo}/metadata/glsa}}). A user can run the {{c|glsa-check}} application to have its system verified against these GLSA notifications and, optionally, update the necessary packages automatically to remediate the vulnerability.

== GLSA可用性 ==

Gentoo Linux安全建议可以通过多种途径获得：

* Chronological Index of GLSA notifications: [https://security.gentoo.org/glsa/ https://security.gentoo.org/glsa/]
* Subscribe to the gentoo-announce@gentoo.org mailing list: [https://www.gentoo.org/get-involved/mailing-lists/ https://www.gentoo.org/get-involved/mailing-lists/]
* GLSA RSS Feed: [https://security.gentoo.org/glsa/feed.rss https://security.gentoo.org/glsa/feed.rss]

